children.text: Stop by the Tye Creek Eatery in the Tye Creek Lodge for a casual lunch experience.
Check out the Pacific Crest Lodge's newly transformed Trailside Snack Shack for ice cream, snacks, and cocoa!
Warm up with espresso drinks, hot beverages, snacks, grab-n-go food and packaged beer and wine. 1st floor of Granite Peaks Lodge.
Iron Goat Pizzeria in the Pacific Crest Lodge is the place for everyone to enjoy traditional and specialty pizzas.
Home of the Foggy Goggle Mug Club, come sit back, have a bite, and enjoy a brew in the Tye Creek Lodge.
Open for lunch and dinner periods in the Granite Peaks Lodge, the Cascadian Kitchen is a perfect pit stop.
On the 2nd floor of the Granite Peaks Lodge. A full-service bar and restaurant with a smokehouse inspired menu for lunch and dinner!
The Biergarten is a fun Bavarian themed dining experience located in the Pacific Crest Lodge.
